                "containerId": null,
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A <em>maestro's instrument</em> can be crafted in the form of any variety of handheld musical instruments. A <em>maestro's instrument</em> grants you a +1 item bonus to Performance checks while playing music with the instrument.</p><hr /><p><strong>Activate—Charming Performance</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> (manipulate)</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You play the instrument, causing it to cast a DC 17 @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Charm] spell.</p><hr /><p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> You must supply a casting of <em>charm</em> of the appropriate rank.</p>"
